Welcome to the International Graduate Center

Your place for MBA and Master Degrees

The IGC supports equality, inclusion and diversity

We promote life changing educational opportunities for people of all
background

   We offer high-quality academic education on Master’s level with strong
   practical relevance, adhering to the high standards of the German
   educational system. In our academic approach we foster intercultural
   awareness, critical thinking and the exchange of ideas in a global
   perspective by providing discussion-oriented seminars in small groups,
   a variety of teaching and assessment methods, and support for
   self-learning processes.



   fulltime programs

What we offer

     * MBA and master programs
     * High-quality academic education
     * Management and leadership with practical relevance
     * Research for practice

     * International MBA - Dual Degree
       You are always going for more? Than choose our International
       MBA program. Become an expert in one of six optional
       specializations.
       1 Year. 2 Countries. 2 Degrees.

          + MBA/MSc
          + EN
          + Full-time
       More information
     * Master in Business Management
       You have an economic background and would like to deepen your
       business knowledge and sharpen your management skills? Study next
       to your job and join our unique program

          + Master of Arts
          + DE & EN
          + Part-time
       More Information
     * Master in European Studies
       Learn about European public management, law, economics and politics
       and get as excited about Europe as we are


          + Master of Arts
          + EN
          + Full-time
       More Information
     * Master of Business Administration
       You are ambitious and want to reach for the stars? Give your career
       a boost and study part-time. Challenging job? Tailor the
       course plan to your needs


          + MBA
          + DE & EN
          + Part-time
       More Information
     * Master in Aeronautical Management
       Fly high with our Aeronautical Management program. Deepen your
       knowledge about the aviation industry. Our professors and lecturers
       have many years of practical experience

          + Master of Engineering
          + EN
          + Full-time
       More Information
     * Master in Cultural Management
       Want to learn about management strategies and methods relevant to
       different cultural areas? Study next to your job and combine theory
       and practice


          + Master of Arts
          + DE
          + Part-time
       More Information
     * European/Asian Management MBA
       Europe or Asia?
       Deepen your management skills and decide later on one of our
       specializations. Visit companies and organizations, become aware of
       cultural differences and become an expert in doing business
          + MBA
          + EN
          + Full-time
       More Information
     * International Tourism Management
       We prepare you to become a leader in the dynamic tourism industry.
       Test your learnings under real conditions on our special tourism
       field trip outside of Germany
          + MBA
          + EN
          + Full-time
